{
  "texts": [
    "The Guided Evolution framework proposed by Morris et al.",
    "also uses LLM to mutate and crossover the code [126].",
    "The main EAs adopted are SPEA-2 [146] and NSGA-II.",
    "SPEA-2 is used to retain elite individuals that performed well in the previous generation.",
    "NSGA-II is used to select individuals for crossover and mutation."
  ]
}